f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a51b4af38bef9919966852e5a081f8864cb6cc","tid":42500,"uid":40994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"果時小學成日見到爸爸叫媽咪入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲次次都入好耐,成日都好想知佢地係入面做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢地有鎖門我成日都轉個門柄轉得好鬼大聲,然後大叫：「媽咪!我好肚餓啊!」佢地隔一陣就會出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於有一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係好奇心驅使下我偷偷地係櫃桶拎左鎖匙,好安靜咁插入去仲勁細力咁轉...門開左,見到佢兩個冇著衫訓左係到,我成個人呆左,唔識比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 媽話即刻用手示意叫我唔好出聲同出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後冇再講過呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd6b3dabaaea20b685e06d254903971932d9642","tid":42500,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個同老豆老母訓，試過幾次訓訓下俾佢兩個仆街搖醒<br />\n<br />\n有次好深刻佢地傳教士緊，跟住老豆線腳一野扒咗係老母到，個下眼尾望到差d ki一聲笑撚咗岀黎好在忍得住唔係就俾佢地發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9a9114e3676bd7d667b7c1bef479b27d092a5571","tid":42500,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>逢禮拜日就啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩條友專登早啲起身以為我唔知 大佬我連老豆10分鐘就完事都知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次搞完又唔記得掉左個袋 我執屋果陣成日要跟手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要用袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔下下中出咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個成日汁到袋，唔知咩黎伸手入去搞到